 </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Autel</supplied> des Héros.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Altar</supplied> of the Heroes.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Altare</supplied> degli Eroi.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>To our knowledge, the heroes are worshipped only at Ain Hofra, see e.g. <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr032200</ref>, <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr032300</ref>.</p>
